          "key_points": [],
          "translation_notes": []
        },
        "scores": {
          "readability": 9.5,
          "accuracy": 8.8
        },
        "issues": [
          {
            "type": "accuracy",
            "description": "英文中的“2x higher”在日常技术语境中通常指“是原来的两倍”（即 200%），而中文的“高出两倍”严格意义上指“增加了 200%”（即达到原来的三倍）。这在性能对比分析中是一个常见的翻译陷阱。"
          },
          {
            "type": "terminology",
            "description": "“frontier”在此处基准测试的语境下，特指吞吐量与交互速度权衡图上的“帕累托前沿”（Pareto frontier）。译文“在整条曲线上”表达很流畅，但略微损失了专业术语的精确度。"
          }
        ]
      },
      "history": []
    },
    {
      "id": "p001",
      "index": 1,
      "source": "Above that tier sits NVIDIA’s B200 and GB200, which outperform MI355X across the frontier. While B200 and GB200 share the same Blackwell compute die, GB200 achieves a higher throughput–interactivity curve because the platform and serving stack reduce non-compute bottlenecks at scale (interconnect/topology, CPU-GPU coupling, and runtime scheduling), translating into effective scale-out and less overhead per token.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0337",
      "parent_block_index": 337,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "Above that tier sits NVIDIA’s B200 and GB200, which outperform MI355X across the frontier. While B200 and GB200 share the same Blackwell compute die, GB200 achieves a higher throughput–interactivity curve because the platform and serving stack reduce non-compute bottlenecks at scale (interconnect/topology, CPU-GPU coupling, and runtime scheduling), translating into effective scale-out and less overhead per token.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "Above that tier sits NVIDIA’s B200 and GB200, which outperform MI355X across the frontier. While B200 and GB200 share the same Blackwell compute die, GB200 achieves a higher throughput–interactivity curve because the platform and serving stack reduce non-compute bottlenecks at scale (interconnect/topology, CPU-GPU coupling, and runtime scheduling), translating into effective scale-out and less overhead per token.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 416,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "凌驾于该梯队之上的是英伟达的 B200 和 GB200，它们在整条曲线上全方位碾压 MI355X。尽管 B200 和 GB200 搭载相同的 Blackwell 计算裸片，但 GB200 推高了吞吐量-交互性曲线。这是因为其平台与 Serving 栈在集群规模下削减了非计算瓶颈（互连/拓扑、CPU-GPU 耦合以及运行时调度），进而转化为高效的横向扩展 (Scale-out)，并摊薄了单 token 的运行开销。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-08T01:10:47.246653",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        }
      },
